}</span> 程序执行路径 <span class="subst">{path}</span>"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    filepath = os.path.join(path, filepath)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> filepath</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
